@startuml
!theme plain
hide footbox
autonumber

actor "APP" as APP
participant "Middleware" as MW
participant "Banco de Comercio" as BDC

title POST /bdc/sub-account?token=<JWT_APP>&tipo=...
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/sub-account?tipo=empresa|p2p
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Generar alias/originId y firma
MW -> BDC: POST /sub-account
BDC --> MW: subcuenta creada / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

@enduml
